WEBVTT

00:01.200 --> 00:04.431
Do you just get up in the morning
and figure out ways to make me crazy?

00:04.600 --> 00:06.238
Is that what you do?
You plot it out?

00:06.400 --> 00:08.038
How can I make Alan
miserable today?

00:08.200 --> 00:09.918
How can I reach into his chest...

00:10.120 --> 00:12.918
...rip out his heart, and suck it dry?

00:14.240 --> 00:16.834
- Mom or ex-wife?
- Ex-wife.

00:17.200 --> 00:19.430
- Hi, Judith.
- Charlie says hello.

00:19.600 --> 00:21.989
She says hi.
You're evil and selfish, you know that?

00:22.960 --> 00:25.030
No, no. L... I think that is
a helpful comment.

00:25.200 --> 00:28.510
I pay you alimony and child support
so that you can have a nice house...

00:28.680 --> 00:31.240
...a nice car, every weekend free
because I've got Jake.

00:31.440 --> 00:35.115
And yet you're telling me
you need a vacation?

00:35.280 --> 00:38.716
Oh, really? Oh, really? And what exactly
is stressing you out, Judith?

00:38.880 --> 00:41.474
Is it the weekly manicure?
The housekeeper?

00:41.640 --> 00:43.517
- Boob lift.
- The boob lift.

00:43.720 --> 00:45.597
- That you paid for.
- That I paid for.

00:45.800 --> 00:48.394
- And never got to see.
- And never got to see.

00:49.880 --> 00:51.472
No, no, no. You listen to me.

00:51.640 --> 00:53.596
I think you live a damn fine lifestyle...

00:53.760 --> 00:55.955
...that I work 60 hours a week
to support.

00:56.120 --> 01:00.113
So if anybody needs a vacation,
it's not you. It's me!

01:00.680 --> 01:02.557
All right, then.

01:03.360 --> 01:04.952
Goodbye.

01:07.200 --> 01:09.794
Judith's going to Hawaii for a week.

01:11.800 --> 01:13.119
So Jake's staying here.

01:13.560 --> 01:15.471
I'm shocked.

